### =============================================================
### AlAshmar API - Halaqas (Classes) Controller
### Base URL: http://localhost:5107
### =============================================================

@baseUrl = http://localhost:5107
@authToken = YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE
@halaqaId = 00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000041
@courseId  = 00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000031

# =============================================================
# HalaqasController  - CRUD
# =============================================================

### Get all halaqas
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/halaqas
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Accept: application/json

###

### Get halaqas by course
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/halaqas/by-course/{{courseId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Accept: application/json

###

### Get halaqa by ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/halaqas/{{halaqaId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Accept: application/json

###

### Create halaqa
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/halaqas
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "className": "Halaqa Al-Fajr",
  "courseId": "{{courseId}}"
}

###

### Update halaqa
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/halaqas/{{halaqaId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "className": "Halaqa Al-Fajr (Updated)"
}

###

### Delete halaqa
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/halaqas/{{halaqaId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

###
